SCHEMA: time/branch.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.time.branch
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic branch lineage artifacts.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record branch
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - branch_id: id
    - parent_save_id: id
    - parent_checkpoint_id: id
    - divergence_tick: u64
    - new_save_id: id
    - reason: text
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Branching creates new lineage only.
- Retroactive mutation in-place is forbidden.
